---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ArticleRewriterGenerator from '../../components/ArticleRewriterGenerator';
import SimilarTools from '../../components/SimilarTools';
---

<Layout title="AI Article Rewriter - AI-Free-Forever">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-indigo-100/50 py-16 mb-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        AI Article Rewriter
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Transform existing content with fresh phrasing while preserving meaning. Generate unique variations of your articles.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ArticleRewriterGenerator client:load />
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Instantly Create Unique, High-Quality Content</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">Need fresh, plagiarism-free content fast? Our AI Article Rewriter transforms existing articles into unique, high-quality pieces that captivate your audience and boost your SEO—without hours of manual rewriting.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Powered by the revolutionary GPT-4o model, the AI Article Rewriter generates natural, engaging content that maintains the meaning of your original article while giving it a fresh new voice. Best of all, it's completely free—no subscriptions, no word limits, and no hidden fees.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Whether you're updating old blog posts, repurposing articles for different platforms, or creating variations for A/B testing, our tool adapts perfectly to your needs.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">How to Rewrite Articles Using the AI Article Rewriter</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Paste Your Article Text</span>
            <p>Copy and paste the article you want to rewrite into the input box.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Select Your Tone, Creativity Level, and Output Length</span>
            <p>Customize your rewritten article to match your audience's expectations by choosing your preferred writing style and tone.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Click "Rewrite Article"</span>
            <p>Generate a polished, completely rewritten version of your article in seconds—ready for immediate use.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Use the AI Article Rewriter?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Avoid Plagiarism and Maintain Originality</h3>
            <p>Create fresh, unique content that passes plagiarism checks while retaining the core message of the original article.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Save Time and Boost Productivity</h3>
            <p>Rewrite full-length articles in seconds instead of spending hours manually paraphrasing and editing.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Repurpose Content Across Platforms</h3>
            <p>Easily adapt articles for different audiences, marketing campaigns, or publishing platforms.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Improve SEO Performance</h3>
            <p>Generate multiple content variations targeting different keyword sets to expand your organic reach and search visibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Who Should Use the AI Article Rewriter?</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Bloggers:</span> Refresh old posts and create multiple content variations for different audiences.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Marketers:</span> Repurpose articles for various platforms, including websites, email campaigns, and social media.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">SEO Specialists:</span> Produce keyword-targeted variations of existing content to dominate multiple search results.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Students:</span> Paraphrase academic papers and research while avoiding plagiarism.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Content Creators:</span> Generate unique content for websites, newsletters, ebooks, and beyond.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Tips for Getting the Best Results When Rewriting Articles</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Best Practice</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Why It Matters</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Choose the right tone</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Match the rewritten article to your target audience's expectations.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Experiment with creativity levels</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Control how closely or loosely the new article follows the original text.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Always review and refine</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Check the rewritten article for clarity, accuracy, and flow before publishing.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Add personal touches</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Enhance the uniqueness by incorporating your insights, examples, and brand voice.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is the AI Article Rewriter really free?</h3>
            <p>Yes! Our tool is 100% free to use, with no word count limits, subscriptions, or hidden fees.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Will the rewritten articles be unique?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Each rewritten article is uniquely generated based on your inputs. However, adding your personal edits enhances authenticity and impact.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I use these articles commercially?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. You can use the rewritten articles for blogs, websites, newsletters, social media, or any other commercial purpose.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How do I ensure the best quality in rewritten articles?</h3>
            <p>Provide clear source text, select the right tone and creativity level, and review the output for accuracy and flow.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How many articles can I rewrite?</h3>
            <p>There's no limit—rewrite as many articles as you need without restrictions.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I rewrite articles in multiple languages?</h3>
            <p>Currently, the AI Article Rewriter supports English. For other languages, you can use a translation tool after rewriting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Choose aiFreeForever's AI Article Rewriter?</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">aiFreeForever (2025)</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Paid Alternatives</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Cost</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">100% Free</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">$29–$99/month</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Word Limits</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Unlimited</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Strict credits or word limits</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">AI Model</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">GPT-4o (Latest)</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Varies (often older models)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Registration Required</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">No</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Yes, with credit card info</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Ease of Use</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Simple and intuitive</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Often complex interfaces</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Tone and Creativity Customization</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Full Control</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Often limited</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Refreshing your content has never been easier. With the AI Article Rewriter, you can instantly create unique, SEO-optimized content that resonates with your audience and supports your business goals—all for free.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-xl text-center mb-8">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold">👉 Start using the AI Article Rewriter today and transform your old content into new opportunities!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <SimilarTools currentToolPath="article-rewriter" category="writing" client:load />
  </main>
</Layout>